ActCanada Wildlife Act
SubjectFor Migratory birds ** Acquisition of lands **
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of the Environment (1) to acquire the lands for the purpose of research, conservation and interpretation in respect of migratory birds; and (2) to dispose of lands within 10 meters of the eastern boundary of the Big Creek National Wildlife Area in Ontario.
